# Portfolio copy conventions

- Do not use the Unicode em-dash (U+2014) in user-visible copy, code comments, or identifiers. Prefer commas, periods, parentheses, or a hyphen-minus (-).
- Missing metric values: use `n/a`, not an em-dash.
- Page title pattern: `"Page | Javier Ramos"`, not em-dash separators.
- Terminal hero log: the `verify lighthouse / CI green` line is intentionally omitted until M6–M8 (real Lighthouse runs + CI). Do not add fabricated verify scores to the terminal block.
